riskcoord,r_habitat_load,threshold,0.7,action,derate,action,stop

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 2: LYAPUNOV WEIGHT CONFIGURATIONS
// V_t = w1*Risk + w2*(1-Coverage) + w3*max(0, Density-MaxDensity)
// Weights must sum to 1.0 for stability guarantees
// ============================================================================

